      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Aug 2025 03:58:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;article id="post-13533" class="post-13533 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized"&gt; 	 	&lt;header class="entry-header"&gt; 		&lt;h1 class="entry-title"&gt;Big Top&amp;#8217;s Big Tub&lt;/h1&gt;	&lt;/header&gt;&lt;!-- .entry-header --&gt;  	&lt;div class="entry-content"&gt; 		 &lt;p&gt;Last Sunday night, I ran into Marina. She said she was going to spend the rest of the day painting pictures.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img fetchpriority="high" width="499" height="280" src="https://www.jvgs.net/accfblog/2025/08/02/big-tops-big-tub/Array" alt="Marina: Speaking of hobbies, I think I'll spend today painting pictures, blurp." class="wp-image-13534" sizes="(max-width: 499px) 100vw, 499px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;That&amp;#8217;s a great hobby for her, because she can use her own ink! 🐙&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;I went bug-hunting, and I continued hunting even after Nook&amp;#8217;s shop closed for the night. I was planning on saving everything for the next day, until I realized&amp;#8230;it was flea market day! So I put a few bugs on display in my house and waited for someone to come in.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="500" height="268" src="https://www.jvgs.net/accfblog/2025/08/02/big-tops-big-tub/Array" alt="Fang: Heya, Jeff! Looks like you've got a real business going on here!" class="wp-image-13538" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;Fang wouldn&amp;#8217;t pay 15k or 13k for a scarab beetle, but he agreed to buy it for 12k. That&amp;#8217;s double what Tom Nook pays! Nice! I normally don&amp;#8217;t sell things on flea market days, but I now see how useful it is during bug-hunting season.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;On Monday night, Antonio gave me a Corinthian post that he had for me, up his nose. I know his nose is big, but I didn&amp;#8217;t think he could fit one of those up his nose! 😛&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="500" height="268" src="https://www.jvgs.net/accfblog/2025/08/02/big-tops-big-tub/Array" alt="Antonio: Whoa... Boy J! Have I got something awesome for YOU, up my nose!" class="wp-image-13539" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;On Thursday night, I listened in on a conversation between Mint and Nana. Nana told Mint that she looked especially lovely today, so she asked how much she spent on cosmetic surgery to look that good. 💀&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="500" height="268" src="https://www.jvgs.net/accfblog/2025/08/02/big-tops-big-tub/Array" alt="Nana: How much money did you spend on cosmetic surgery?" class="wp-image-13540" sizes="auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;That made Mint furious, understandably. She said it was the face she got from her parents.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Poor Biskit was sick with a cold lately, so I gave him some medicine on Thursday and again tonight. Get well soon, Biskit!&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Tonight, I headed over to the Roost for K.K. Slider&amp;#8217;s Saturday night show. I asked for a random song (as I typically do), and he performed &amp;#8220;K.K. Dixie&amp;#8221; for me.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="500" height="268" src="https://www.jvgs.net/accfblog/2025/08/02/big-tops-big-tub/Array" alt="K.K.: All right, get ready to dig the riffs on this ditty: K.K. Dixie." class="wp-image-13541" sizes="auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;I later spotted a tarantula on the shore, and even in the water!&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="500" height="262" src="https://www.jvgs.net/accfblog/2025/08/02/big-tops-big-tub/Array" alt="A tarantula standing in the water." class="wp-image-13542" sizes="auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;I approached him slowly, and he wasn&amp;#8217;t moving. So I was able to catch him without much trouble.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Big Top asked me for a fossil, so I gave him a fern fossil that I dug up. He rewarded me with a library wall, and he said he felt like he had just eaten a big tub of happiness! Aww!&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="500" height="281" src="https://www.jvgs.net/accfblog/2025/08/02/big-tops-big-tub/Array" alt="Big Top: Awwww, shucks... I feel like I've just eaten a big tub of happiness." class="wp-image-13543" sizes="auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /&gt;&lt;figcaption class="wp-element-caption"&gt;Big Top&amp;#8217;s big tub.&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;But despite all that happiness, Big Top was thinking about moving out of town! However, I kept talking to him until I was able to change his mind. He&amp;#8217;s staying. 😮‍💨&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Just today, I posted the latest City Folk Moments video! Check it out!&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"&gt;&lt;div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"&gt; &lt;iframe loading="lazy" title="ACCF - City Folk Moments #28 (Animal Crossing)" width="660" height="371" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/57ZbxUqnNFQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;    &lt;p&gt;The first (of five) fireworks festivals is tomorrow night. Have fun if you&amp;#8217;ll be playing, and enjoy the show! 🎆&lt;/p&gt; 	&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .entry-content --&gt;  	 	&lt;footer class="entry-footer"&gt; 		&lt;span class="posted-on"&gt;&lt;span class="screen-reader-text"&gt;Posted on &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.jvgs.net/accfblog/2025/08/02/big-tops-big-tub/" rel="bookmark"&gt;&lt;time class="entry-date published" datetime="2025-08-02T23:58:00-04:00"&gt;August 2, 2025&lt;/time&gt;&lt;time class="updated" datetime="2025-08-03T01:58:29-04:00"&gt;August 3, 2025&lt;/time&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="byline"&gt;&lt;span class="screen-reader-text"&gt;Author &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="author vcard"&gt;&lt;a class="url fn n" href="https://www.jvgs.net/accfblog/author/jvgsjeff/"&gt;Jeff&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;			&lt;/footer&gt;&lt;!-- .entry-footer --&gt;  &lt;/article&gt;</description>
